PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 1990-07851990-04-260,  ,  OLD INAC,  , 
PrecisOrder which provides for (a) the transfer to the Province of British Columbia of the administration and control over some 17.10 hectares of land situated on Lachkaltsap Indian Reserve No. 9 and Andegulay Indian Reserve No. 8 (in lieu of the taking of those lands without consent of the owners), and (b) for the setting apart of some 20.48 hectares of provincial land for the use and benefit of the Lakalzap Band of Indians as an addition to Lachkaltsap Indian Reserve No. 9.
